item.title: Snooping in WHonix???
item.dc:creator: Ego
item.description:
Good day,

why do you automatically presume someone would “have joined you”? That’s just a system intern function. The “bell” is just a “emergency notification” used by a lot of Linux’s.

Have a nice day,

Ego
